em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"margin-left:-10px;display:inline-block;padding-left:30px;width:auto;font-size:16px;border-bottom-right-radius:100px;line-height:40px;height:40px;padding-right:30px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔥 本周热门</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">React 基金会成立</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;—— 这几年，React 的“归属权”和“控制权”一直是社区讨论的焦点，大家总担心如果哪天发生变动会怎么办。在 React Conf 2025 上，官方宣布 React 及 React Native 的管控权将从 Meta 交接到一个独立的基金会，初期成员包括 Amazon、Expo、Meta 和 Microsoft 这些大厂，后续更开放和社区共建。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, se